Dexia’s Asset-Management Unit Isn’t for Sale, Belga Reports

-- B y   A n d r e w   C l a p h a m
-- 
2011-10-11T06:57:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/dexia-s-asset-management-unit-isn-t-for-sale-belga-reports.html
Dexia SA (DEXB) ’s asset-management unit
isn’t for sale as part of the group’s restructuring, Belga
reported, citing SETCa union member Jean-Michel Cappoen.  “The sale scenario wouldn’t be on the table,” the
newswire quoted Cappoen as saying. Dexia prefers to take more
time analyzing the situation to assess which ties with the bank
can be maintained, according to Belga.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Clapham in Brussels at 
 aclapham@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net  